 </div> 
</div> 
<p><strong>Aspects of the Crucible: Breath</strong> is an <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Incantations" href="/Incantations" target="">Incantation</a> in <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Wiki" href="/Elden+Ring+Wiki">Elden Ring</a>. <strong>Aspects of the Crucible: Breath spell</strong> allows you to throw fire while walking.</p> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<div class="lineleft"> 
 <p><em>One of the ancient Erdtree incantations.</em><br><br><em>Creates a throat pouch on the caster's neck, allowing them to spew</em><br><em>fiery breath while walking.</em><br><em>Charging increases duration of the breath.</em><br><br><em>This is a manifestation of the Erdtree's primal vital energies - an</em><br><em>Aspects of the primordial crucible, where all life was once blended</em><br><em>together.</em></p> 
</div> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 class="bonfire">Where to find Aspects of the Crucible: Breath</h3> 
<ul> 
 <li>By&nbsp;<strong>Rykard, Lord of Blasphemy</strong>&nbsp;Site of Grace in&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Volcano Manor" href="/Volcano+Manor">Volcano Manor</a>: Progress&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Tanith" href="/Tanith">Tanith</a>'s quest to the point where she's feasting on&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Rykard" href="/Rykard">Rykard</a>'s corpse, then kill her. <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Tanith's Knight" href="/Tanith's+Knight">Tanith's Knight</a>&nbsp;will invade shortly thereafter, and will drop this&nbsp;<strong>Aspects of the Crucible: Breath</strong> when killed. [<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Interactive Map?id=4597&amp;lat=-87.085937&amp;lng=66.979244&amp;zoom=8&amp;code=mapA" href="/Interactive+Map?id=4597&amp;lat=-87.085937&amp;lng=66.979244&amp;zoom=8&amp;code=mapA">Map Link</a>]</li> 
 <li><a class="wiki_link" title="Video Location" href="https://youtu.be/gjx27iqiG8c?t=5807">Video Location</a></li> 
</ul> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 class="bonfire">Elden Ring&nbsp;Aspects of the Crucible: Breath Guide</h3> 
<ul> 
 <li>Stamina Cost: 40</li> 
 <li>Can be charged in order to spew flames for a longer duration at the cost of continuous FP depletion.</li> 
 <li>It is possible to move and turn while casting.&nbsp;</li> 
 <li>Deals Fire damage and is affected by fire damage buffs.</li> 
 <li>Recieves a 3.5% damage bonus for each worn piece of the <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Crucible Axe Set" href="/Crucible+Axe+Set">Crucible Axe Set</a>&nbsp;and <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Crucible Tree Set" href="/Crucible+Tree+Set">Crucible Tree Set</a>.</li> 
</ul> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
